            . I am an officer. I asked the prisoner how much money he had about him; he said, a three-shilling piece; he took out his box, and there were two three-shilling pieces in it. Mrs. Rowley said, she can prove the three-shilling piece; she paid it to Mrs. Grace on Saturday night.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It was impossible for me to take it and put it in my box, without the people in the shop seeing me; that three-shilling piece is my own.</p>
